main event: Multiple witnesses observed 7 UFOs in Clewiston, Florida on the night of May 18, 1968.
interesting points: Witnesses reported seeing the objects descend in formation,The UFOs were described as having colored lights and unusual maneuvers,The observation lasted between 10:00 and 10:50 PM,All objects were observed through binoculars,The tape recording of the observation was ruined for unknown reasons, prompting witnesses to seek advice and form a club for future observations.
witness description: names of witnesses were not disclosed
